page.title: 09A typical day of the Carre's
page.content: My name is Brian Carre and on Saturday my mum,dad,sister Sarah and myself all get dressed and have our breakfast and take our dogs for a run at Les Landes. The dogs are called Hiedi and Tishca and they sometimes catch a rabbit but its usually Hiedi that catches it. When we get home we have our lunch and watch television and I clean my ferret's cage out and feed my fish and my tadpoles then we all sit down and have a rest. Sometimes my dad goes to Mr. M's to plough the fields or scarify them and sometimes I go with him and sit on the back of the tractor. While we are at Mr. M's my mum cleans the house and my sister goes out to play.
